<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="16May1937"><font color="red">16 May 1937</font> <i>NLJL</i> (from Paul L&eacute;on to G. Wren Howard): I beg to acknowledge receipt of your favours from the 26th of April and 5th and 14th inst. I have gone through the first batch of queries with Mr Joyce himself and am enclosing together with the results of carefully reading the pages 369-373. I will go through the new queries with Mr Joyce to morrow or the day after and I will send them to you without further delay. </div>
